nodes.text: Headliner was a YT-1220, that was owned by the Tourism Council of Oluna Biqua during the Clone Wars. It was used as an in-system shuttle in the Cularin system and was piloted by Dellko, a Rodian. The Council sent it to take the Heroes of Cularin to Oluna Biqua, as they were going there for a luxury holiday. On arrival there, it was told to land at Port Epsilon, which it did.
